OL,3,CPeople with autism and learning
OL,4,Cdisabilities 'locked up' in hospitals
OL,6,FPeople with learning disabilities are
OL,7,Fbeing "locked up" in hospitals instead
OL,8,Fof being supported in their
OL,9,Fcommunities, according to a campaign
OL,10,Fgroup.
OL,12,FCampaigners say a shortage of
OL,13,Fappropriate housing and support for
OL,14,Fpeople with autism and learning
OL,15,Fdisabilities means some are being
OL,16,Fseparated from their families.
