OL,3,CPeople with autism and learning
OL,4,Cdisabilities 'locked up' in hospitals
OL,6,FThe Stolen Lives group launched a
OL,7,F'Homes Not Hospitals' petition outside
OL,8,Fthe Senedd on Wednesday, 17 April, and
OL,9,Fsay people with disabilities "had
OL,10,Falways been a forgotten group".
OL,12,FThe Welsh Government denies people are
OL,13,Fbeing held "inappropriately".
OL,15,F140 people with a learning disability
OL,16,Fare being treated in specialised
OL,17,Finpatient services in Wales and
OL,18,FEngland, according to the Welsh
OL,19,FGovernment.
