OL,3,CPeople with autism and learning
OL,4,Cdisabilities 'locked up' in hospitals
OL,6,FThe parents of an autistic man who was
OL,7,Fsectioned while in independent living
OL,8,Faccommodation have told ITV Wales he
OL,9,Fhas been left traumatised by the
OL,10,Fexperience.
OL,12,FJanis and Matthew Griffiths' son
OL,13,FWilliam was sectioned in 2019. They
OL,14,Fwere eventually able to bring him
OL,15,Fhome, but they are campaigning to try
OL,16,Fand stop this from happening to anyone
OL,17,Felse with similar needs.
