OL,3,CPeople with autism and learning
OL,4,Cdisabilities 'locked up' in hospitals
OL,6,FJanis said when William gets the right
OL,7,Fcare there are very few issues and he
OL,8,Fis able to go abroad and enjoy
OL,9,Fsocialising.
OL,11,FShe said: "He's lovely. When he meets
OL,12,Fyou he'll want to know about you.
OL,14,F"He'll ask you about your birthday,
OL,15,Fyour children, your pets and all the
OL,16,Frest of it.
OL,18,F"Then, 10 years later when you see him
OL,19,Fagain he'll ask: 'How's your dog?'
