OL,3,CPeople with autism and learning
OL,4,Cdisabilities 'locked up' in hospitals
OL,6,F"He'll still remember those details
OL,7,Fabout you. He's fascinating from that
OL,8,Fpoint of view. He's very easy, he's
OL,9,Fnot much of a problem at all."
OL,11,FJanis says she can't undo the trauma
OL,12,Fof what William went through when he
OL,13,Fwas sectioned, but she wants somebody
OL,14,Fto pay attention to how people are
OL,15,Ftreated.
OL,17,FWilliam's dad Matthew said: "It was
OL,18,Fdeeply traumatic for all those
OL,19,Finvolved. He still exhibits symptoms
OL,20,Fof PTSD.
