OL,6,F"We would take him out and he would
OL,7,Fstill keep saying 'why have they done
OL,8,Fthis to me? Why can't I go back? What
OL,9,Fhave I done wrong?'
OL,11,F"He was just awful and we took him out
OL,12,Fand he would tell us stories.
OL,13,FObviously you have to believe what he
OL,14,Fsays with care but I believe some of
OL,15,Fwhat he says was true.
OL,17,F"They were dreadful circumstances."
