OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We take the care
OL,7,Fof vulnerable people very seriously
OL,8,Fand are committed to reducing the
OL,9,Fnumber of people with a learning
OL,10,Fdisability who are housed in a
OL,11,Fhospital setting.
OL,13,F"We do not agree that people are being
OL,14,Fsystematically detained
OL,15,Finappropriately in mental health units.
