OL,6,F"When people with a learning
OL,7,Fdisability are occasionally admitted
OL,8,Fto a mental health unit, it is vitally
OL,9,Fimportant they receive care
OL,10,Fappropriate to meet their individual
OL,11,Fneeds.
OL,13,F"This means that they must have a care
OL,14,Fplan, which is reviewed regularly and
OL,15,Fdischarge planning and options around
OL,16,Ffuture accommodation needs are fully
OL,17,Fconsidered.
