OL,6,FSpeaking in the Senedd, Mark
OL,7,FIsherwood, Conservative MS for North
OL,8,FWales and chair of the Senedd cross-
OL,9,Fparty groups on autism and disability,
OL,10,Fsaid: "There has been a learning
OL,11,Fdisability strategy in place in Wales
OL,12,Fsince 2018, which seeks to ensure that
OL,13,Fautistic people or people with a
OL,14,Flearning disability who are in long-
OL,15,Fterm placements are discharged and
OL,16,Fable to live their lives in the
OL,17,Fcommunity.
