OL,6,F"However, Learning Disability Wales
OL,7,Fstates that 'approximately 150
OL,8,Fautistic people or people with a
OL,9,Flearning disability are known to be in
OL,10,Fa hospital setting, over two thirds
OL,11,Ffor over 10 years', although numbers
OL,12,Fdon't include all people and all
OL,13,Fsettings.
OL,15,F"We therefore need to know why such a
OL,16,Fhigh number are still in long-term
OL,17,Fhospital placements. I call for a
OL,18,Fstatement accordingly."
